{"tid":247930,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登有愛] 想r豪宅住","createTime":"2017-05-18T07:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T03:29:10.000Z","uid":28870,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b9d74d518d5b7d92847b632453d6868f8e5db3dc","tid":247930,"uid":28870,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T07:32:33.000Z","msg":"是咁的 本身想係香港體驗吓個上樓服務 <br />\n但成10000蚊先1呎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nWtsapp左問朋友 大家都話好唔抵 不如開po r樓住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n...<br />\n所以想問吓連登巴絲有冇人有豪宅可以住吓<br />\n唔會白住你 可以幫你抹翻地/煮餐飯仔你食<br />\n白住人地樓好似不是太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲可做吓好心 <br />\n好想試吓住豪宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果凱旋門就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以打卡po ig fb等啲朋友羨慕下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e0b18d216acb136aabd86661a5cbe65b416872","tid":247930,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T07:33:29.000Z","msg":"Pthm (Part time housemate)?"},{"pid":"b29c9898d6bd6397d69b156042a0a8d2393c72c3","tid":247930,"uid":56508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T07:33:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> in連登we trust"},{"pid":"a552f2debadaf58eabe71cb78a489a2a65bd7fde","tid":247930,"uid":33336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T07:35:45.000Z","msg":"你可以拎個閪出黎交租實得"},{"pid":"d97ce6382b015bf25380ad19153b826cd068de11","tid":247930,"uid":23897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T07:50:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你可以拎個閪出黎交租實得</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agr